1305
01:45:40,668 --> 01:45:41,710
One...

1306
01:45:46,715 --> 01:45:47,758
...two...

1307
01:45:51,762 --> 01:45:52,847
...three.

1308
01:46:44,815 --> 01:46:46,609
Come on.

1309
01:46:57,411 --> 01:46:58,829
Son of a bitch.

1310
01:46:59,830 --> 01:47:02,207
-Christ, he stinks.
