1312
01:47:05,377 --> 01:47:08,088
My face! Give me back my face!

1313
01:47:08,923 --> 01:47:11,550
<i>The masked vigilante Rorschach
was apprehended...</i>

1314
01:47:11,717 --> 01:47:15,554
<i>...and identified
as Walter Kovacs, a 35-year-old white male.</i>

1315
01:47:15,721 --> 01:47:18,807
<i>Little's known about Kovacs,
but he was charged with the murder...</i>

1316
01:47:18,974 --> 01:47:22,811
<i>...of Edgar Jacobi, found shot in the head
in his home in the Bronx.</i>

1317
01:47:22,978 --> 01:47:26,023
<i>Police officers were injured
and Jacobi's home was set ablaze...</i>

1318
01:47:26,190 --> 01:47:28,734
