1319
01:47:32,529 --> 01:47:33,864
Rorschach!

1320
01:47:34,031 --> 01:47:37,743
I'm gonna fuck you
like I fucked your mother!

1321
01:47:44,375 --> 01:47:47,336
Come on out, Rorschach!

