1427
01:57:09,898 --> 01:57:12,359
What evidence have you got?
That's nothing.

1428
01:57:20,283 --> 01:57:23,078
Okay. I confess.

1429
01:57:24,287 --> 01:57:26,957
I kidnapped her. I killed her.

1430
01:57:27,749 --> 01:57:29,125
Arrest me.

1431
01:57:29,960 --> 01:57:31,670
